 用&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL29wZW53YWxsL2pvaG4vYmxvYi9ibGVlZGluZy1qdW1iby9ydW4vZGVlcHNvdW5kMmpvaG4ucHk=&#34;&gt; https://github.com/openwall/john/blob/bleeding-jumbo/run/deepsound2john.py&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
deepsound2john.py 脚本&lt;br /&gt;
